\\u00c2\", \"from\": 6382, \"to\": 6383}, {\"ngram\": \"the quartet\", \"from\": 6408, \"to\": 6419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murphy and Fink had good opening splits, but not quite as fast as they were Saturday on the front end of the mixed medley\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094they were a combined 1.04 seconds slower, which loomed large in a race decided by .55 seconds.\", \"from\": 6507, \"to\": 6725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Murphy\", \"from\": 6507, \"to\": 6513}, {\"ngram\": \"Fink\", \"from\": 6518, \"to\": 6522}, {\"ngram\": \"good opening splits\", \"from\": 6527, \"to\": 6546}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 6583, \"to\": 6591}, {\"ngram\": \"the front end\", \"from\": 6595, \"to\": 6608}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed medley\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094they\", \"from\": 6612, \"to\": 6635}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 6695, \"to\": 6701}, {\"ngram\": \".55 seconds\", \"from\": 6713, \"to\": 6724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressel had a monster fly leg, clocking a 49.41, but that didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t provide quite enough cushion for Armstrong going up against China\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Pan Zhanle, who smashed his own world record in the 100 free earlier in the meetin an eyebrow-raising 46.40 seconds.\", \"from\": 6727, \"to\": 6980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6827, \"end\": 6836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.916292495614367e-26, \"text\": \"Armstrong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 6727, \"to\": 6734}, {\"ngram\": \"a monster fly leg\", \"from\": 6739, \"to\": 6756}, {\"ngram\": \"quite enough cushion\", \"from\": 6802, \"to\": 6822}, {\"ngram\": \"China\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 6854, \"to\": 6863}, {\"ngram\": \"Pan Zhanle\", \"from\": 6864, \"to\": 6874}, {\"ngram\": \"his own world record\", \"from\": 6888, \"to\": 6908}, {\"ngram\": \"the meetin\", \"from\": 6936, \"to\": 6946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pan followed that up with what might be the fastest relay split in human history, dropping a 45.92 to win the race\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s .14 faster than Jason Lezak\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s immortal 100 free split for the U.S. in the 2008 Olympics that kept Michael Phelps\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 drive for eight gold medals alive.\", \"from\": 6981, \"to\": 7259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pan\", \"from\": 6981, \"to\": 6984}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest relay split\", \"from\": 7021, \"to\": 7044}, {\"ngram\": \"human history\", \"from\": 7048, \"to\": 7061}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 7087, \"to\": 7106}, {\"ngram\": \"Jason\", \"from\": 7123, \"to\": 7128}, {\"ngram\": \"immortal 100 free split\", \"from\": 7139, \"to\": 7162}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 7167, \"to\": 7175}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2008 Olympics\", \"from\": 7179, \"to\": 7196}, {\"ngram\": \"Michael Phelps\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 drive\", \"from\": 7207, \"to\": 7230}, {\"ngram\": \"eight gold medals\", \"from\": 7235, \"to\": 7252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given China\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s drug history, this was not an overwhelmingly popular result.\", \"from\": 7261, \"to\": 7337, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drug history\", \"from\": 7277, \"to\": 7289}, {\"ngram\": \"an overwhelmingly popular result\", \"from\": 7304, \"to\": 7336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Twenty-three swimmers had positive tests for Trimetazidine in 2021,which was revealed in the spring, and there have been revelations about other positive tests that were kept secret and yielded no penalties.\", \"from\": 7338, \"to\": 7545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7383, \"end\": 7396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trimetazidine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trimetazidine\", \"types\